description:
This is a 59 minute workout called 'Beginners Marathon Training | 60 Min Treadmill Run | Fitscope Studio' from the channel Fitscope.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/Running.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Beginners Marathon Training | 60 Min Treadmill Run | Fitscope Studio

Join Antonio for this long guided treadmill run including stretching, walking and inclines.  Great for marathon or spartan training.  Even though its long, good for beginners and experienced runners alike.
